title: Quadrantids Meteor Shower
description: The Quadrantids is an above average meteor shower, producing up to 40 meteors per hour at its peak.

title: Venus at Greatest Eastern Elongation
description: Venus reaches greatest eastern elongation of 47.2 degrees from the Sun. Look for it in the western sky after sunset.

title: Full Moon - Wolf Moon
description: This full moon was known as the Wolf Moon. Occurs at 22:28 UTC.
